OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,FThe family of Linda Nolan have invited
OL,7,Ffans of the pop star to attend her
OL,8,Ffuneral.
OL,10,FLinda, who was part of the band The
OL,11,FNolan Sisters, died on 15 January
OL,12,Ffollowing a long battle with cancer at
OL,13,Fthe age of 65.
OL,15,FThe funeral will be held on Saturday 1
OL,16,FFebruary at St Paul's Church in
OL,17,FBlackpool, where Linda married her
OL,18,Fhusband Brian Hudson in 1981.
