OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,FLinda's siblings extended the
OL,7,Finvitation to her fans on Instagram,
OL,8,Fencouraging them to attend her
OL,9,Fmemorial service at the church and pay
OL,10,Ftribute to her memory.
OL,12,FOn the Nolans official Instagram page,
OL,13,Fthey said: "The Nolan family invites
OL,14,Feveryone to join them in celebrating
OL,15,Fthe extraordinary life of Linda Nolan,
OL,16,Fwho passed away peacefully on January
OL,17,F15, 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
