OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,F"Linda was a beacon of light, strength
OL,7,Fand unwavering love who inspired
OL,8,Feveryone she met, in addition to
OL,9,Fmillions around the world.
OL,11,F"Her absence leaves an ache in our
OL,12,Fhearts, but her legacy will live on
OL,13,Fthrough the joy, hope and kindness she
OL,14,Fshared so freely. Linda's funeral
OL,15,Fservice will take place on Saturday,
OL,16,F1st February 2025, at St. Paul's
OL,17,FChurch, Honister Avenue, Blackpool, at
OL,18,F10.30am.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
