OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,F"Everyone who knew Linda, or whose
OL,7,Flives she touched, are welcome to come
OL,8,Fand pay their respects as we remember
OL,9,Fher remarkable life.
OL,11,F"Fans and public are welcome to gather
OL,12,Foutside the church for the funeral -
OL,13,Fand in true Linda spirit, the more the
OL,14,Fmerrier!
OL,16,F"St. Paul's Church holds a deeply
OL,17,Fspecial place in Linda's heart. It is
OL,18,Fwhere she married the love of her
OL,19,Flife, Brian Hudson, with whom she
OL,20,Fshared 26 wonderful years of marriage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
