OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,F"Brian was Linda's rock, her soulmate,
OL,7,Fand the love of her life, just as she
OL,8,Fwas his.
OL,10,F"When Brian tragically passed away in
OL,11,F2007, Linda found the strength to
OL,12,Fcarry on, but her love for him never
OL,13,Fwavered. St. Paul's was also where
OL,14,FLinda said her final goodbye to Brian,
OL,15,Fholding his funeral in the same church
OL,16,Fwhere they had exchanged their vows.
OL,18,F"Now, Linda will return to this sacred
OL,19,Fplace to be reunited with Brian once
OL,20,Fmore, finally at peace and back in his
OL,21,Floving embrace."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
