OL,3,C'The more the merrier!' Linda Nolan
OL,4,Cfans invited to attend her funeral
OL,6,FThey added: "Linda was more than a
OL,7,Fbeloved sister, friend, and
OL,8,Fentertainer - she was a symbol of
OL,9,Fhope, humour and resilience."
OL,11,FThere will be a private cremation at a
OL,12,Fnearby crematorium after the service,
OL,13,Ffor close family and friends only.
OL,15,FThe family of Linda have created a
OL,16,Fmemorial page in hopes of raising as
OL,17,Fmuch money as possible for Trinity
OL,18,FHospice, a charity that held a special
OL,19,Fplace in Linda's heart.
